16:14.740 --> 16:17.243 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
"NewsHour" special correspondent
Nick Schifrin
is in Havana reporting for us
this week, joins

16:17.276 --> 16:18.244 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
