country.

16:46.439 --> 16:49.942 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And at least along the route
today, that image
of him really survives.

16:49.976 --> 16:53.512 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: There aren't a
