same exact
words, my leader, my father.

17:00.286 --> 17:05.358 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And even critics of Fidel Castro
say that
those sentiments are genuine
after so many

17:05.391 --> 17:06.692 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
