believed in
human rights.

17:20.539 --> 17:25.111 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And the granddaughter,
23-year-old Gizelle
Gallego (ph), said that the
revolution should

17:25.144 --> 17:30.149 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
